<s> a representative from the fire protection command of the fire services department gave talks and shared his experience on three topics , namely " causation of fire and some notable fire cases in hong_kong " , " fire prevention and fire escape " and " fire services installations and its maintenance " . </s>
<s> an instructional video on building repairs and maintenance was shown . </s>
