<s> following is the transcript ( english part ) of the remarks by the financial secretary , mr donald tsang , at a media session after attending a special provisional legislative council meeting this ( tuesday ) evening : </s>
<s> fs : i just explained to the legislative councillors the reason behind my decision that we should be prepared to lend to the thai central bank up to us $ 1 billion . </s>
<s> i explained to them that the history of the case , particularly that the problem which the thai government faced since may this year and how it eventually developed into a crisis in july and particularly , </s>
<s> i also explained to them that there are intrinsic advantages for hong_kong . there are immediate advantage of saving the thai baht . </s>
<s> in medium term , </s>
<s> and hong_kong forms part of the region . </s>
<s> there must be direct benefit to hong_kong to ensure the problem in thailand will not spread to other countries and will not create a problem eventually for hong_kong . </s>
<s> and finally , as an international financial centre , </s>
<s> i do no think we can sit on our hands , </s>
<s> i think we should come forward with a contribution which is appropriate in the circumstances , not excessive but not miniscule and i think we have taken the right decision . </s>
<s> thank you very much . </s>
