<s> over 3,000 students go for central allocation </s>
<s> a total of 3,071 students have today ( tuesday ) applied for central allocation to fill the remaining 121 secondary six ( s 6 ) places . </s>
<s> the education department reminded applicants to check at the centres where they applied for central allocation and the district education offices on saturday ( august 16 ) to see if they have been allocated a place . </s>
<s> application results will be displayed at 9 am . successful candidates should register with the allocated school before 1 pm on the same day . </s>
<s> places were allocated on the basis of the applicants ' hong_kong certificate of education examination results under central allocation at stage five . </s>
<s> if students are unable to secure a place after the completion of stage five , they may still be able to get a place at the beginning of the new school year because some successful students may decide not to take up their places . </s>
<s> a list of schools with s 6 vacancies will be displayed and updated weekly at all district education offices throughout september . </s>
<s> students should apply to these schools direct but admission will be entirely at the schools ' discretion . meanwhile , no complaint concerning schools not following the admission procedure has been received by the department . </s>
<s> the department 's central hotline 2892 5786 , 2892 5785 and 2892 5751 and the 19 district education offices handled about 99 and 397 enquiries respectively on the admission procedure today . </s>
<s> this brings to 569 and 2,709 the total number of enquiries made at the hotline and the district education offices . </s>
<s> trade figures involving outward processing in mainland china </s>
<s> in the first quarter of 1997 , 48 % of hong_kong 's total exports to the mainland of china were for outward processing ; the figure was 71 % for domestic exports , </s>
<s> and 45 % for re @-@ exports . on the other hand , </s>
<s> 75 % of hong_kong 's imports from the mainland of china were related to outward processing , according to statistics released today ( tuesday ) by the census and statistics department . </s>
<s> over the same period , 85 % of hong_kong 's re @-@ exports of origin from the mainland of china to other places were produced through outward processing in the mainland of china . </s>
<s> the corresponding proportions for exports to the mainland in the first quarter of 1996 were 43 % for total exports , </s>
<s> 71 % for domestic exports and 39 % for re @-@ exports . </s>
<s> proportions for imports from the mainland and for re @-@ exports of origin from the mainland to other places were 82 % and 86 % respectively . </s>
<s> the scope of the survey has been extended to cover hong_kong 's imports from the mainland and hong_kong 's re @-@ exports of origin from the mainland to other places from 1989 and 1991 respectively . </s>
<s> the results for the first quarter of 1997 are available . </s>
<s> in value terms , $ 51.3 billion of hong_kong 's total exports to the mainland in the first quarter of 1997 were for outward processing , representing an increase of 13 % over the first quarter of 1996 . </s>
<s> the value of domestic exports to the mainland for outward processing decreased by 1 % to $ 8.8 billion whilst the value of re @-@ exports to the mainland for outward processing rose by 16 % to $ 42.5 billion . </s>
<s> over the same period of comparison , the value of imports from the mainland related to outward processing dropped by 1 % to $ 96.8 billion . </s>
<s> on the other hand , $ 121.2 billion of hong_kong 's re @-@ exports of origin from the mainland to other places were produced through outward processing in the mainland , </s>
<s> representing an increase of 4 % . </s>
<s> the estimates for the first quarter of 1997 and the corresponding changes over the same period in 1996 are summarised in the following table : </s>
<s> estimated value and proportion of trade involving outward processing in the mainland of china , 1 st quarter of 1997 </s>
<s> total value of trade with the mainland of china * : </s>
<s> total exports to the mainland 107,497 + 2.1 </s>
<s> domestic exports 12,415 - 1.6 </s>
<s> re @-@ exports 95,082 + 2.6 </s>
<s> imports from the mainland 128,482 + 7.3 </s>
<s> re @-@ exports of origin from the mainland to other places 142,999 + 5.3 </s>
<s> estimated value involving outward processing in the mainland of china : </s>
<s> total exports to the mainland 51,340 + 12.9 </s>
<s> domestic exports 8,813 - 1.2 </s>
<s> re @-@ exports 42,527 + 16.3 </s>
<s> imports from the mainland 96,779 - 1.4 </s>
<s> re @-@ exports of origin from the mainland to other places 121,167 + 3.9 </s>
<s> estimated proportion involving outward processing in the mainland of china : </s>
<s> total exports to the mainland 47.8 43.2 </s>
<s> domestic exports 71.0 70.6 </s>
<s> re @-@ exports 44.7 39.5 </s>
<s> imports from the mainland 75.3 81.9 </s>
<s> re @-@ exports of origin from the mainland to other places 84.7 85.9 </s>
<s> * the value excludes commodities and transactions not classified according to kind . </s>
<s> for the purpose of the survey , </s>
<s> exports to the mainland for outward processing refer to raw materials or semi @-@ manufactures exported from or through hong_kong to the mainland for processing with a contractual arrangement for subsequent re @-@ importation of the processed goods into hong_kong . </s>
<s> imports from the mainland related to outward processing refer to processed goods imported from the mainland , of which all or part of the raw materials or semi @-@ manufactures have been under contractual arrangement exported from or through hong_kong to the mainland for processing . </s>
<s> re @-@ exports of origin from the mainland to other places involving outward processing in the mainland refer to processed goods re @-@ exported through hong_kong , </s>
<s> of which all or part of the raw materials or semi @-@ manufactures have been exported from or through hong_kong to the mainland for processing with a contractual arrangement for subsequent re @-@ importation of the processed goods into hong_kong . </s>
<s> in interpreting the statistics , </s>
<s> a sample of trade declarations in respect of hong_kong 's trade with the mainland and hong_kong 's re @-@ exports originated in the mainland to other places is selected for enumeration to obtain the required information from the establishments concerned . </s>
<s> a spokesman for the census and statistics department explained that all imports and exports of goods ( not including transhipments and goods @-@ in @-@ transit ) are recorded as external trade , </s>
<s> irrespective of whether the goods are associated with outward processing or not . </s>
<s> the findings of the survey , however , facilitate a more informed analysis of the nature of hong_kong 's trade with the mainland . </s>
<s> in this respect , the survey results are a useful supplement to the regular trade statistics . </s>
<s> the above survey results will be included in the june 1997 issue of the " hong_kong external trade " . </s>
<s> the report will be on sale by the end of august 1997 at the government publications centre , queensway government offices , low block , ground floor , 66 queensway , and at the publications unit of the census and statistics department , 19 th floor , </s>
<s> enquiries on the survey results may be directed to the trade surveys and research section of the census and statistics department on telephone 2565 7540 . </s>
<s> a new general out @-@ patient clinic set up by the department of health in tung chung will commence operation on thursday ( august 14 ) to provide primary health care service to the public . </s>
<s> " local residents will benefit from better medical and health services with the opening of the new clinic , </s>
<s> the new clinic , tung chung general out @-@ patient clinic , is located on the first floor of tung chung health centre at 6 fu tung street , tung chung on lantau island . </s>
<s> the opening hours are from 9 am to 1 pm and 2 pm to 5 pm on weekdays , and 9 am to 1 pm on saturdays . no service will be provided on sundays and public holidays . </s>
<s> on the other hand , the travelling dispensary in tung chung will cease to operate on the same day ( thursday ) . </s>
