<s> school @-@ based support scheme grant for schools </s>
<s> public sector schools with an intake of new arrival children ( nac ) from the mainland are invited to apply for the newly introduced school @-@ based support scheme grant ( the grant ) . </s>
<s> a senior education officer , mr li che @-@ cheung , </s>
<s> said , " a block grant will be given to public sector schools upon application under the school @-@ based support scheme . " the scheme aims to strengthen the support for schools with an intake of new arrival children . </s>
<s> " it also enables them to flexibly design programmes to cater for these children . </s>
<s> " applicant schools will be given a block grant at the rate of $ 2,000 per new arrival child at primary one to six levels and $ 3,330 at secondary one to seven levels , </s>
<s> " mr li said . </s>
<s> in order to enable schools to provide timely support services to help nac , </s>
<s> the education department is prepared to disburse two advance payments , one in october 1997 and the other in january 1998 , to schools upon application . </s>
<s> heads of schools are requested to make a reasonable and accurate estimate of nac to be admitted on which advance payments are based . </s>
<s> " such advance payment will be adjusted at a later date according to the actual number of nac admitted during the specified period , " mr li said . </s>
<s> schools should note that they can only apply for the grant in respect of those nac who satisfy the following criteria : </s>
<s> * the period between the date of entering hong_kong and the first day of attending the applicant school is less than one year ; </s>
<s> * no previous claim has been made in respect of the child ; and </s>
<s> * the child should remain registered as a pupil of the applicant school on the date of confirmation on the actual number of new arrival children admitted . </s>
<s> schools are also required to keep a separate account for the grant to reflect all the income and expenditure chargeable to it , he added . </s>
<s> mr li noted that the grant can be used to conduct supplementary lessons for new arrival children , </s>
<s> purchase teaching aids and resource materials and organise orientation , guidance programmes or extra @-@ curricular activities . </s>
<s> other activities can be run provided that the grant is used for the benefit of the new arrival children and that the services should be provided as soon as they are admitted into the school , </s>
<s> school heads who intend to apply for the first advance payment of the grant for the period april 1 to october 31 , </s>
<s> 1997 should return complete proforma to the general administration section of the department 's services division , at room 1106 , wu chung house , </s>
<s> 213 queen 's road east , wan chai , by mail or by fax number 2834 7350 on or before september 19 ( friday ) , 1997 . </s>
<s> late applications will not be accepted . </s>
<s> parents who wish to apply for a primary one place in public @-@ sector schools for their children in september next year under the primary one admission system can obtain application forms from today ( monday ) to september 26 . </s>
<s> " application for participation in the primary one admission system for school entry in september 1998 was open to all hong_kong belonging children who were born on or before 31 december 1992 , except those who were attending primary schools or those who had been allocated a primary one place previously , </s>
<s> " senior education officer , mrs pak au tak @-@ chuen , said . </s>
<s> parents of children attending kindergartens may obtain the application form , an information leaflet and explanatory notes on how to complete the application form from their kindergartens , mrs pak said . </s>
<s> for parents of children not attending kindergartens , the form is available at district offices ( public enquiry service centre ) and offices of the education department , she added . </s>
<s> mrs pak stressed that the completed application form together with all the supporting documents should be submitted within school office hours between september 22 to september 26 direct to a government or aided primary school in which the parent wished to apply for a discretionary place . </s>
<s> this school might either be within or outside the school net in which the child resided . </s>
<s> parents are strongly advised to select a school in their neighbourhood in order to reduce unnecessary transport problems and to take the " points system " into consideration when selecting the school , mrs pak said . </s>
<s> mrs pak emphasised that only one application form should be submitted in respect of any one child . </s>
<s> " if parents are found to have applied to more than one government or aided school , their applications will be rendered void and no discretionary place will be allocated , " she said . </s>
<s> she also requested parents of children who could not use chinese as a learning medium to seek advice from the school places allocation section ( primary one admission ) on the second floor , 269 queen 's road east , wan chai , </s>
<s> hong_kong before submitting application forms . they may also call 2832 7700 . </s>
<s> she further pointed out that schools receiving too few applications for discretionary places may not be allowed to operate primary one classes . </s>
<s> in such cases , children already secured discretionary places in these schools would have to be subsequently re @-@ allocated to some other schools which had vacancies . </s>
<s> if parents wish to apply for the central allocation only , they should submit their completed application forms with the supporting documents to one of the following collection centres within office hours during the same period ( septmeber 22 to september 26 ) : </s>
<s> second floor , lui kee education services centre , 269 queen 's road east , wan chai , hong_kong </s>
<s> * education department kowloon sub @-@ office on the 7 th floor , kowloon government offices , 405 nathan road , kowloon </s>
<s> * sha tin district office , </s>
<s> public enquiry service centre on the first floor , citylink plaza , 1 sha tin station circuit , sha tin </s>
<s> * tai po district office , </s>
<s> public enquiry service centre on the ground floor , tai po government offices building , ting kok road , tai po </s>
<s> * tsuen wan district office , </s>
<s> public enquiry service centre on the first floor , tsuen wan station , multi @-@ storey carpark building , 174 @-@ 208 castle peak road , tsuen wan </s>
