<s> speaking to the press at the airport , </s>
<s> ms wong said she had had a " useful and frank " exchange of views with vietnamese officials from the immigration department of the ministry of interior , the consular department of the ministry of foreign affairs and the office for refugee and repatriation affairs of the ministry of labour , invalids and social affairs . </s>
