<s> as well as active participation in wipo activities in which economies such as hong_kong , which are not sovereign states , can take part separately . </s>
<s> commenting on the meeting in geneva , mr selby said : </s>
<s> " taking part as a member of the chinese delegation has been very interesting . </s>
